{
  "texts": [
    "Search terms included \"artificial intelligence,\" \"machine learning,\" \"data mining,\" \"intelligent tutoring system,\" \"robotics,\" \"learning management system,\" and \"e-learning\" combined with \"Nigerian education system\" or \"Nigerian institutions\" from 2008 to 2022.",
    "Inclusion criteria were limited to papers related to AI in education in Nigeria and popular AI technologies in education elsewhere, published between 2008 and 2022.",
    "Only proceedings papers or peer-reviewed journal articles were included to ensure relevance and accuracy.",
    "Empirical and theoretical works using quantitative or qualitative approaches were considered.",
    "Exclusion criteria encompassed animal studies, non-English articles, non-empirical data, incorrect study design, and no usable data."
  ]
}